properties.areaDesc: Admiralty Inlet Area; Everett and Vicinity
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 1 at 3:12AM PST until February 1 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph.

* WHERE...Everett and Vicinity and Admiralty Inlet Area.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL INFORMATION...This wind advisory replaces the high
wind warning, which is no longer in effect.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM PST THIS MORNING
